OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fmostly die out this evening but a few
OL,7,Fcontinuing across Argyll overnight.
OL,8,FOtherwise becoming dry but persistent
OL,9,Frain will spread from the southwest
OL,10,Flater on.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Flocally heavy rain during the morning.
OL,14,FBecoming drier in the afternoon with
OL,15,Fjust a few showers.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,18,Fof locally heavy rain on Friday. Early
OL,19,Fshowers on Saturday then dry. Dry and
OL,20,Fbright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
